data.meta_description: Bolesław III "Wry Mouth" Piast, Duke of Poland was born on August 20, 1085 in Kraków, Małopolskie, Poland, son of Władysław I Herman, Duke of Poland and Judith of Bohemia., they gave birth to 1 child. He died on October 28, 1138 in Sochaczew, Sochaczew County, Masovian Voivodeship, Poland. This information is part of Family tree Cromer/Russell/Buck/Pratt by Elizabeth Cromer on Genealogy Online.
